00:02:06.620 --> 00:02:09.900
Nasty Gal's amazing, you
could do so much with this,

00:02:09.900 --> 00:02:13.660
and I was like, I don't know,
a book seems really cool,

00:02:13.660 --> 00:02:15.322
but I don't know.

00:02:15.322 --> 00:02:17.030
