literary department at WME,

00:02:19.770 --> 00:02:21.450
I can't make anything
happen for you,

00:02:21.450 --> 00:02:24.200
but all I can do is
make the introduction

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:26.500
and if something
happens then great.

00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:29.300
And he did, and I had
a meeting with someone

00:02:29.300 --> 00:02:32.270
who works for her, who is
now kind of like my fairy

00:02:32.270 --> 00:02:35.220
godmother at WME.

00:02:35.220 --> 00:02:36.987
And we had one
meeting and she said,

00:02:36.987 --> 00:02:38.070
what would you want to do?

00:02:38.070 --> 00:02:41.960
The obvious thing would be to
do a style book, a hardcover

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:43.940
coffee table book.

00:02:43.940 --> 00:02:47.060
And I was like, I don't know,
I mean that's so expected.

00:02:47.060 --> 00:02:49.580
And it's not because I wanted
to do something unexpected,

00:02:49.580 --> 00:02:53.390
it's just because a business
book would be really fun.

00:02:53.390 --> 00:02:55.540
And there's a lot
of stories that I

00:02:55.540 --> 00:02:59.480
hadn't told about my experience
to reporters in the media,

00:02:59.480 --> 00:03:01.610
because what am I going
to do, tell Forbes

00:03:01.610 --> 00:03:02.849
that I was a dumpster diver?

00:03:02.849 --> 00:03:04.390
Like what's the
headline going to be?

00:03:04.390 --> 00:03:07.810
So it was cool to
tell my own story

00:03:07.810 --> 00:03:10.450
and also I really
kind of set out

00:03:10.450 --> 00:03:12.530
to write a book that
was, in some way,

00:03:12.530 --> 00:03:14.920
like the gateway
drug to the business

00:03:14.920 --> 00:03:17.250
section of the
bookstore, for someone

00:03:17.250 --> 00:03:22.474
who may not be going there
yet, because I was that girl.

00:03:22.474 --> 00:03:23.890
And I think there's
a lot to learn

00:03:23.890 --> 00:03:26.179
in that part of the bookstore.

00:03:26.179 --> 00:03:27.720
FEMALE SPEAKER: So
that's interesting

00:03:27.720 --> 00:03:29.761
that you say that that's
sort of the gateway drug

00:03:29.761 --> 00:03:31.700
to like a book about
business or management,

00:03:31.700 --> 00:03:33.140
because when you
see the cover it

00:03:33.140 --> 00:03:35.390
doesn't look like a book
about business, right?

00:03:35.390 --> 00:03:38.220
It's "#Girlboss," I mean, yeah,
it has the word boss in it,

00:03:38.220 --> 00:03:41.667
but what made you
pick that title,

00:03:41.667 --> 00:03:43.250
at what point did
you pick that title,

00:03:43.250 --> 00:03:45.120
what does it mean
