persona, are they the same

00:03:51.974 --> 00:03:52.890
or are they different?

00:03:52.890 --> 00:03:55.190
SOPHIA AMORUSO: Good questions.

00:03:55.190 --> 00:03:59.750
So, I named Nasty Gal
after an album and a song

00:03:59.750 --> 00:04:02.590
by a lady named
Bette Davis, and I

00:04:02.590 --> 00:04:05.970
don't know, just
in that same vein,

00:04:05.970 --> 00:04:07.470
really I'm not inventing names.

00:04:07.470 --> 00:04:10.750
So there's a film, a
very little known film,

00:04:10.750 --> 00:04:13.960
called "Girl Boss Guerrilla"
from the '70s that's

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:18.410
like a Japanese
female revenge flick,

00:04:18.410 --> 00:04:21.110
and it's really
stylish, really good.

00:04:21.110 --> 00:04:25.215
It's like girl gangs knife
fighting in the streets.

00:04:25.215 --> 00:04:27.900
It's just so cool, and they
have a tattoo over their,

00:04:27.900 --> 00:04:31.719
like, right boob or something.

00:04:31.719 --> 00:04:33.260
So it's called "Girl
Boss Guerrilla,"

00:04:33.260 --> 00:04:35.960
and I just loved the name, and
I was just like, "#Girlboss."

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:37.960
I don't know, it was never
called anything else,

00:04:37.960 --> 00:04:41.470
there were no alternate
names, it was just kind of

00:04:41.470 --> 00:04:42.720
really simple.

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:46.500
And then how do you
differentiate a Girl Boss

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:47.930
