and Girl Boss gives them,

00:04:57.570 --> 00:04:59.920
hopefully, the tools to do it.

00:04:59.920 --> 00:05:03.750
So I would say, the
ethos is very similar.

00:05:03.750 --> 00:05:07.630
Nasty Gal is a fashion
brand, first and foremost,

00:05:07.630 --> 00:05:13.610
and I think Girl Boss right now
is a book, [AUDIO OUT] cast.

