00:07:28.170 --> 00:07:30.400
FEMALE SPEAKER: And so,
what I'm curious about

00:07:30.400 --> 00:07:35.560
is, was there a
moment that showed

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:38.770
you, that demonstrated that,
