00:07:43.780 --> 00:07:45.620
SOPHIA AMORUSO:
Yeah, absolutely.

00:07:45.620 --> 00:07:49.120
I don't ever use the
term, I've made it,

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:52.110
and I get that a lot like,
when did you made it?

00:07:52.110 --> 00:07:55.460
Making it, I think, is just,
like that's an everyday thing,

00:07:55.460 --> 00:07:57.440
because if I thought
I'd made it I'd probably

00:07:57.440 --> 00:08:00.260
