your back to the ocean.

00:08:07.010 --> 00:08:09.730
But there was a
time, and there's

00:08:09.730 --> 00:08:13.910
different moments over
the course of Nasty Gal's

00:08:13.910 --> 00:08:16.550
trajectory, I think,
that were symbols

00:08:16.550 --> 00:08:20.420
