I mean I own most
of the company,

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:49.990
technically I
control the company,

00:10:49.990 --> 00:10:53.852
and I have as much
creative input as I want.

00:10:53.852 --> 00:10:55.810
One thing we're spending
a lot of time on right

00:10:55.810 --> 00:10:58.870
