for our creative team,

00:10:58.870 --> 00:11:00.387
for anyone that
touches the brand

00:11:00.387 --> 00:11:02.970
to understand what the brand is,
to know how to use the brand,

00:11:02.970 --> 00:11:05.790
what the parameters
are, where you can play.

00:11:05.790 --> 00:11:08.240
But over the course
of the last--

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:11.290
I mean since I've had a team
that are making decisions

00:11:11.290 --> 00:11:14.270
on Nasty Gal's behalf, whether
