someone else's opinion

00:11:40.280 --> 00:11:41.740
about what's right
for the brand,

00:11:41.740 --> 00:11:44.710
rather than this is what
it is, it lives here,

00:11:44.710 --> 00:11:49.390
let me self-reflect before
