more objective,

00:11:53.177 --> 00:11:55.260
and that's something we're
doing a lot of work on,

00:11:55.260 --> 00:11:57.030
is getting this kind
of like brand bible,

00:11:57.030 --> 00:11:59.880
I guess, to get out of my head
the things that make Nasty

