00:20:14.640 --> 00:20:17.200
because that has to become
systematic at a certain point.

00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:19.200
It starts with hiring
people who care,

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:22.590
who take pride in what they
do, who are open to feedback

00:20:22.590 --> 00:20:28.280
and want to learn, and who
want to tweak out on their work

00:20:28.280 --> 00:20:30.890
rather than show up
and just like, OK

00:20:30.890 --> 00:20:33.200
put the jacket on the
model, what time is it,

00:20:33.200 --> 00:20:36.320
I'm leaving now, you know?

